quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  3,149,"Hey mon yo goŇč…óim…ďe, si on …óoftike …ďen heefer…ďe, …ďe ruttay on e batte [kaaferaaku] mon, waylito…óon ko on hayru…ďe(pertube)."
  3,150,"Si ko woni, ko Alla woni Gi…óo mon, ko KaŇčko woni …ďur…óo mo∆ī∆īu…óo e walloo…ďe …ďe."
  3,151,"Arma Men mberoo kulol e nder …ďer…óe …ďen heefer…ďe, sabu ko …ďe kafidi Alla e kon ko O Jippinanaali hujja. Jaa∆īnde ma…ď…ďe ko ka yiite, bonii jaa∆īnde …ďen too√Īoo…ďe."
  3,152,"GoŇč…óii Alla Goonginanii on Fodoore Makko nden tuma nde warayno…óon …ďe e DuŇčayee Makko, haa nde cooy…óon lurru…óon e fiyaake …óen, yeddu…óon …ďaawo o hollii on ko yi…óu…óon. No e mon …ďen faalaa…ďe aduna, no e mon kadi …ďen faalaa…ďe laakara. Hooti O Yiili on e ma…ď…ďe fii yo O Ndaarndo on. GoŇč…óii O Yaafanike on. Alla ko Jom ∆Āural e dow goŇč…óim…ďe …ďen."
  3,153,"Tuma nde dogayno…óon on ye∆ī∆īitaako hay e gooto, Nulaa…óo on no noddira on …ďaawo mon. Suno e hoore suno he…ďi on fii wata on cuno e kon ko laawii on wanaa e kon ko he…ďi on. Alla ko kumpitii…óo e ko. Ngolloton ko"